quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  19,96,aur jo log imaan laaye aur amal naik kiye khuda un ki mohabbat ( makhloqaat ke dil mein ) peda kardey ga
  19,97,( ae paighambar ) hum ne yeh ( quran ) tumhari zabaan mein aasaan ( nazil )kiya hai taakay tum is se parhaiz garon ko khushkhabri pouncha do aur chugralo-own ko dar suna do
  19,98,aur hum ne is se pehlay bohat se garohoon ko halaak kardiya hai. bhala tum un mein se kisi ko dekhte ho ya ( kahin ) un ki bhanak suntay ho
  20,1,Taa-Haa
  20,2,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) hum ne tum par quran is liye nazil nahikiya ke tum mushaqqat mein par jao
  20,3,balkay is shakhs ko nasiyaat dainay ke liye ( nazilkiya hai ) jo khauf rakhta hai
  20,4,yeh is ( zaat bartar ) ka utaara howa hai jis ne zameen aur ounchay ounchay aasman banaye
  20,5,( yani khuday-e ) rehman jis ne arsh par qarar pakra
  20,6,jo kuch asmano mein hai aur jo kuch zameen mein hai aur jo kuch un dono ke beech mein hai aur jo kuch ( zameen ki ) matti ke neechay hai sab isi ka hai
  20,7,aur agar tum pukaar kar baat kaho to woh to chupay bhaid aur nihayat posheeda baat taq ko jaanta hai
  20,8,( woh mabood brhq hai ke ) is ke siwa koi mabood nahi hai. is ke ( sab ) naam achay hain
  20,9,aurkiya tumhe moose ( ke haal ) ki khabar mili hai
  20,10,jab unhon ne aag dekhi to apne ghar walon se kaha ke tum ( yahan ) thehro mein ne aag dekhi hai ( mein wahan jata hon ) shayad is mein se mein tumahray paas angraai lau ya aag ( ke maqam ) ka rasta maloom karsakeoon
  20,11,jab wahan puhanche to aawaz aayi ke moose
  20,12,mein to tumhara perwar-digaar hon to apni jotiyan utaar do. tum ( yahan ) pak maidan ( yani ) tawee mein ho
